<h2 id="chords-progressions">Chords progressions</h2>

<p>Tempo is ~105 beats per minute. Each of the five verses uses a nearly identical chord progression, whether you’re playing fingerstyle (verse 1) or strumming (verses 2-5). Notice how in verses 3-5, measures #10 and #15 change their length, based on lyrical context. Also, the A-minor that ends each verse is the same as the A-minor that starts the verse that follows (in all cases, stay on this A-minor for two measures total).</p>

<p>Verse #1 - “Hello darkness, my old friend”</p>

